data.description: This thoughtfully designed two-story home offers 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and spans 2,182 square feet. Ideal for families, it features a spacious kitchen with a pantry, extra storage under the stairs, granite countertops, and a large kitchen island. The open concept kitchen and living area are perfect for entertaining, while the main bedroom offers a sizable walk-in closet. Upstairs, discover 3 bedrooms, a game room, and a full bath. The home also includes a covered patio, smart home technology, and a full sod sprinkler system. Don’t miss the chance to make this your perfect family home – schedule a viewing today!
